                </div>

                <div id="stage1-analysis" class="tab-content active">
                    <div class="worksheet-section">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Is your market truly unsophisticated?</label>
                        <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="Analyze: Has your target audience been exposed to similar products or claims? Are you truly first?"></textarea>
                        <div class="worksheet-hint">Be honest‚Äîmost markets aren't truly at Stage 1</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="worksheet-section">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">What is the core need/claim?</label>
                        <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="State the primary benefit in its simplest form..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

