                    </div>

                    <div class="worksheet-section">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Why this works for Stage 1</label>
                        <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="Explain why this headline is appropriate for an unsophisticated market..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- STAGE 2 -->
        <div class="stage-section">
            <div class="stage-header">
                <div class="stage-badge">
                    <div class="stage-badge-label">Stage</div>
                    <div class="stage-badge-num">02</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stage-content">
                    <h2>The Enlarged Claim</h2>
                    <p class="stage-subtitle">Outbid Your Competition with Bigger Promises</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">üéØ</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">The Strategy</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <strong>Copy the successful claim but enlarge upon it.</strong>
                        <p style="margin-top: 12px;">Once competitors enter, the original direct claim still works, but mere repetition isn't enough. Drive the claim to the absolute limit of believability to outbid your competition.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">üìù</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">When to Use</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Competitors have copied the original claim</li>
                            <li>The basic promise is familiar to prospects</li>
                            <li>Market still believes in the core benefit</li>
                            <li>You need to differentiate through magnitude</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">‚ö°</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">How to Execute</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Add specific numbers and timeframes</li>
                            <li>Make the result bigger or faster</li>
                            <li>Include guarantees or risk reversals</li>
                            <li>Push to believability's edge (but don't cross it)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="example-box">
                <div class="example-label">Classic Example Headline</div>
                <div class="example-text">"LOSE UP TO 47 POUNDS IN 4 WEEKS‚ÄîOR RECEIVE $40 BACK!"</div>
                <div class="example-explanation">Takes the weight loss claim and enlarges it with specific numbers, timeframe, and a money-back guarantee.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="worksheet">
                <div class="worksheet-header">
                    <div class="worksheet-icon">‚úçÔ∏è</div>
                    <h3 class="worksheet-title">Your Stage 2 Headline</h3>
                </div>

                <div class="tabs">
                    <button class="tab active" onclick="switchTab(event, 'stage2-analysis')">Market Analysis</button>
                    <button class="tab" onclick="switchTab(event, 'stage2-headline')">Your Headline</button>
                </div>

                <div id="stage2-analysis" class="tab-content active">
                    <div class="worksheet-section">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">What is the competing claim?</label>
                        <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="Identify what your competitors are promising..."></textarea>
                    </div>

                    <div class="worksheet-section">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">How can you enlarge it?</label>
                        <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="Think: more, faster, easier, guaranteed... What's the believable limit?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="stage2-headline" class="tab-content">
                    <div class="worksheet-section">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Stage 2 Headline</label>
