                        <div class="worksheet-hint">Include specific numbers, timeframes, or guarantees</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="worksheet-section">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Why this outbids competitors</label>
                        <textarea class="worksheet-input" placeholder="Explain how your claim is bigger/better while remaining believable..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- STAGE 3 -->
        <div class="stage-section">
            <div class="stage-header">
                <div class="stage-badge" style="background: var(--accent-secondary);">
                    <div class="stage-badge-label">Stage</div>
                    <div class="stage-badge-num">03</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stage-content">
                    <h2>The New Mechanism</h2>
                    <p class="stage-subtitle">The Most Important Stage for Modern Advertisers</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">üéØ</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">The Strategy</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <strong>Shift emphasis from WHAT to HOW.</strong>
                        <p style="margin-top: 12px;">The market becomes glutted and skeptical. Claims are automatically discounted. You must introduce a NEW MECHANISM to make the old promise fresh and believable again.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">üìù</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">When to Use</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Market is saturated with claims</li>
                            <li>Prospects are skeptical of promises</li>
                            <li>Claims are automatically discounted</li>
                            <li>You need to revive interest in the benefit</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">‚ö°</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">How to Execute</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Feature the mechanism, not just the result</li>
                            <li>Explain HOW the product works</li>
                            <li>Introduce a unique process or ingredient</li>
                            <li>Make the mechanism the star of the headline</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="example-box">
                <div class="example-label">Classic Example Headlines</div>
                <div class="example-text">"FLOATS FAT RIGHT OUT OF YOUR BODY!"</div>
