                    <h2>Embellishing the Mechanism</h2>
                    <p class="stage-subtitle">Making It Quicker, Easier, or Surer</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">üéØ</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">The Strategy</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <strong>Elaborate or enlarge upon the successful mechanism.</strong>
                        <p style="margin-top: 12px;">Just as in Stage 2, competitors adopt your mechanism, leading to a new cycle of elaboration. Make the mechanism seem quicker, easier, or more certain.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">üìù</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">When to Use</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Competitors have copied your mechanism</li>
                            <li>The mechanism is now familiar to prospects</li>
                            <li>Market still believes in the process</li>
                            <li>You need to enhance the mechanism's appeal</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">‚ö°</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">How to Execute</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Add qualifiers to the mechanism</li>
                            <li>Make it easier or faster</li>
                            <li>Remove limitations or barriers</li>
                            <li>Enhance with "first," "only," or "new"</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="example-box">
                <div class="example-label">Classic Example Headline</div>
                <div class="example-text">"FIRST NO-DIET REDUCING WONDER DRUG!"</div>
                <div class="example-explanation">Takes the "wonder drug" mechanism and embellishes it by removing the limitation (dieting).</div>
            </div>

            <div class="worksheet">
