        <!-- STAGE 5 -->
        <div class="stage-section">
            <div class="stage-header">
                <div class="stage-badge" style="background: var(--accent-tertiary);">
                    <div class="stage-badge-label">Stage</div>
                    <div class="stage-badge-num">05</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stage-content">
                    <h2>The Exhausted Market</h2>
                    <p class="stage-subtitle">Identification Over Product Performance</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">üéØ</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">The Strategy</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <strong>Shift away from product to prospect identification.</strong>
                        <p style="margin-top: 12px;">The market no longer believes in promises or mechanisms. You must bring the prospect into the ad by reflecting their personality, problems, or desires.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">üìù</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">When to Use</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Market is completely saturated</li>
                            <li>Prospects believe nothing you say</li>
                            <li>Field is considered "exhausted"</li>
                            <li>Product attributes no longer matter</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="info-card">
                    <div class="info-card-header">
                        <div class="info-card-icon">‚ö°</div>
                        <h3 class="info-card-title">How to Execute</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card-content">
                        <ul>
                            <li>Focus on the prospect's identity</li>
                            <li>Address their emotional state</li>
                            <li>Reflect their aspirations or fears</li>
                            <li>Use lifestyle or status positioning</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="example-box">
                <div class="example-label">Classic Example Headlines</div>
                <div class="example-text">"WHY MEN CRACK..."</div>
                <div class="example-text" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 12px;">Marlboro: Virile Men Visual Ads</div>
                <div class="example-explanation">Addresses a human condition or identity rather than product attributes. Revives "dead" products through identification.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="worksheet">
                <div class="worksheet-header">
